'''Dodecian''' was a military title of the [[Givin/Legends|Givin]] leader of the [[Body Calculus]]. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], [[Illiet]] was Dodecian of the [[Yag-prime]] [[Space station/Legends|space station]], and had the authority to demand the surrender of the ''[[Stalking Moon]]''. Dodecians apparently painted their exoskeletons with mathematical symbols.

